= Sample Usage

Set up a standard CouchDB service :

    couchdb {'couchdb': }

Set up an alternate CouchDB service with a different service name :

    couchdb {'couchdb-feat':
        port    => 5985,
    }

(This only works with a modified couchdb package that allows symlinking
 the service script to run with a different configuration)
